<pre class="r"><code>df = cbind(fit = if_else(previsao==&quot;br&quot;,1,0), class = if_else(test$book==&quot;br&quot;,1,0)) %&gt;% as.data.frame()
plot_pred_type_distribution(df,0.5)</code></pre>
